info.author: Sean Reifschneider
info.description:
The second generation of the JOTWeb web application system.  It uses Zope 3's
TAL engine to render dynamic pages for web sites.  Includes result caching using
memcached, if available, to increase overall performance.
info.name: jotweb2
info.html_description: The second generation of the JOTWeb web application system. It uses Zope 3’s TAL engine to render dynamic pages for web sites. Includes result caching using memcached, if available, to increase overall performance.
